16–18, Epigynum (16, ventral; 17, lateral; 18, posterior). 19–21, Female habitus (19, dorsal; 20, frontal; 21, lateral). Voucher: 16–21, (DZUB 8699). Scale bars: genitalia, 0.25 mm; other drawings, 1 mm.
